      "index": "b4h",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1880034694,
      "version": 179,
      "versionNonce": 86528410,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779965263924,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "How can we improve pagination consistency and efficiency?\n     ❌ Timestamp-based cursors \n        - WHERE published_at < cursor_timestamp ORDER BY published_at DESC LIMIT 20\n        - multiple articles have identical timestamps\n        - we might miss articles that share the exact same timestamp\n    ✅  Monotonically increasing article ID\n        - WHERE article_id < cursor_id ORDER BY article_id DESC LIMIT 20\n        - need to use ULID or database auto-increment",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How can we improve pagination consistency and efficiency?\n     ❌ Timestamp-based cursors \n        - WHERE published_at < cursor_timestamp ORDER BY published_at DESC LIMIT 20\n        - multiple articles have identical timestamps\n        - we might miss articles that share the exact same timestamp\n    ✅  Monotonically increasing article ID\n        - WHERE article_id < cursor_id ORDER BY article_id DESC LIMIT 20\n        - need to use ULID or database auto-increment",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
