      "text": "How do we handle traffic spikes during breaking news?\n    - vast majority of traffic focuses on regional content - Americans want US news, Europeans want EU news\n    - deploy infrastructure close to users in each region",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How do we handle traffic spikes during breaking news?\n    - vast majority of traffic focuses on regional content - Americans want US news, Europeans want EU news\n    - deploy infrastructure close to users in each region",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
